    "chinese": "请问，有菜单吗？我想要一杯茶。你们有什么特色菜？我要一碗米饭，一盘青菜。这个菜辣吗？请不要放辣椒。买单，谢谢！",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "chinese": "请问，有菜单吗？",
        "english": "Excuse me, do you have a menu?"
      },
      {
        "chinese": "我想要一杯茶。",
        "english": "I would like a cup of tea."
      },
      {
        "chinese": "你们有什么特色菜？",
        "english": "What are your specialty dishes?"
      },
      {
        "chinese": "我要一碗米饭，一盘青菜。",
        "english": "I want a bowl of rice and a plate of vegetables."
      },
      {
        "chinese": "这个菜辣吗？",
        "english": "Is this dish spicy?"
      },
      {
        "chinese": "请不要放辣椒。",
        "english": "Please don't add chili peppers."
      },
      {
        "chinese": "买单，谢谢！",
        "english": "The bill, please!"
      }
    ]
  },
